title: Pinto Coelho (Jacinto)
body: He was born in Funchal on October 7, 1847, and is the brother of the previous entry. For many years, he was a private primary education teacher, and on December 18, 1884, he was appointed temporary aspirant of the Funchal Customs, currently holding the position of sub-inspector in this fiscal establishment. He has collaborated in a large number of local newspapers, and more recently in the Diario de Noticias, his articles being noted for the correctness and elegance with which they are always written (1921).

Jacinto Pinto Coelho: Teacher, sub-inspector of the Funchal Customs

1884: Appointment as temporary aspirant of the Funchal Customs
